item.title: Parenting: Am I Stuffing This Up? with Psychoanalyst, Andy Cohen
item.description: In this week's Podcast We ask some important Questions: "Am I standing in the way of my parenting? Am I Over-thinking it?" With our guest, Psychoanalyst & Psychotherapist, Andy Cohen, we discuss the basics of parenting - from the joy of becoming parents, to the complexity of anxiety. Andy's latest book, "Parenting Psychoanalysed: Letters to a Parent," is launching in May. To secure your pre-order, send an email to this address: andy@globalmicro.co...
